## Handles * representations:
##
## 	rep* is special
##         rep shows all possible languages
##
## Revision 1.2  1999/03/08 06:34:07  peterg
## Removed mtt help - replaced by grep #SUMMARY - quicker
##
## Revision 1.1  1998/10/20 08:15:08  peterg
